title: L'Oreal Paris Infallible Never Fail Concealer, Medium
description: Infallible never fail concealer fights the five signs of concealer meltdown for 16 hours of flawless coverage. Creamy stick formula blends easily for up to 16 hours of transfer-proof coverage. Won’t cake, mask, or crease and won’t fade or change color.

title: The Brush Guard Variety Pack
description: The Brush Guard is an entirely new brush care product which allows brushes to be washed and then dried in the best way possible: bristles down, and then stored with the vulnerable bristles protected.  The Brush Guard is a new, patented product which takes brush care to a whole new level of easy, effective hygiene.  Visit our website for more information: thebrushguard.com
